data.description: Your dream home awaits you, come enjoy a beautiful evening on your patio or barbeque with family and friends or take advantage of the many local dining options, come see the views from this contemporary Gem that sits on a conner lot with lots of mature trees plenty of shade or enjoy a cup of coffee in the morning Enjoying the natural reserve park. Also, the covered patio makes a great area to entertain or watch football with friends. Close to 1604,151, I10 and minutes away from SeaWorld, six flags, and great shopping center LA. Cantera. Also, outdoor include multiple terraces and a level 25x60 area ready for your own projects numerous upgrades, including fans and lighting, custom touches in the primary bath, water softener, and under sink reverse osmosis, vaulted ceilings and a built-in bar. Seller to Help with some closing costs.property has access to Tennis courts,basketball and pool.
